cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.SE

The paper investigates the security of connected lighting systems, which involves wireless communication and network protocols. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves penetration testing and vulnerability analysis, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.SE (Software Engineering). The paper also discusses the wireless range of the systems, which falls under cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
